@startuml
title UML state machine diagram

state "Create Account" as CreateAccount
CreateAccount : entry/User wants to create account
CreateAccount : do/Fill details
CreateAccount : exit/Registration successful

state "Watch Videos" as WatchVideos
WatchVideos : entry/User logged in
WatchVideos : do/Watch videos
WatchVideos : exit/Continue watching

state "Upload Video" as UploadVideo
UploadVideo : entry/User wants to upload video
UploadVideo : do/Upload video
UploadVideo : exit/Video uploaded

state "Save Video" as SaveVideo
SaveVideo : entry/During video viewing
SaveVideo : do/Save video in likes list
SaveVideo : exit/Video saved

state "View Saved Videos" as ViewSavedVideos
ViewSavedVideos : entry/User wants to view saved videos
ViewSavedVideos : do/Show saved videos
ViewSavedVideos : exit/Completed viewing

state "Enter Discussion" as EnterDiscussion
EnterDiscussion : entry/User wants to enter discussion option
EnterDiscussion : do/Enable discussion
EnterDiscussion : exit/Discussion started

CreateAccount --> WatchVideos
WatchVideos --> UploadVideo
UploadVideo --> SaveVideo
SaveVideo --> ViewSavedVideos
ViewSavedVideos --> EnterDiscussion
@enduml
